content: Will there be a public server of the Real Number Game similar to the Natural Number Game? Or is Real Number Game still in development?
We'd be happy to add it to our server if somebody (maybe you?) would port it.
The real number game never really existed. I don't think anyone ever worked out a coherent real number game.
Sounds like it was just an imaginary number game
Oh we do have a complex number game! It doesn't use the game engine but there's no reason why it shouldn't.
